						[% for (var valueNo = -1; ++valueNo &lt; values.length;) { %]

						[% } %]
					&lt;/ul&gt;
				
[% /* ]]&gt; */ %]
           </script>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
        <input name="hs" type="hidden" value="true"/>
        <a class="ZazzleWwwSearchInput-searchButton" id="page_zazzleHeader_headerSearch-searchButton">
         <i class="zazzicon zazzicon-search">

        </a>
       </form>

                           [% /* &lt;![CDATA[ */ %]

				values = input.values,

					ZazzleOptionsSelector-option

						false

			&gt;

             <h4 class="ZazzleWidgetsSppProductDesktop-templateShellTitle">
              Edit this design template
             </h4>
             <div class="" id="page_product-templateUi">
              <div class="ZazzleForm ZazzleTemplateFieldsUi ZazzleWidgetsSppTemplate " id="page_product_template">
               <form accept-charset="UTF-8" class="" id="page_product_template-form" method="post" name="template" novalidate="novalidate">
                <div class="" id="page_product_template_elements">
                 <div class="ZazzleSeeMoreUi ZazzleSeeMoreUi-contentsFit ZazzleSeeMoreUi-collapsed" id="page_product_template_seeMore">
                  <div class="ZazzleSeeMoreUi-containerShell" id="page_product_template_seeMore-containerShell" style="max-height:315px">
                   <div class="" id="page_product_template_seeMore-container">
                    <div class="ZazzleTemplateFieldsUi-scrollyFields" id="page_product_template-elementsShell">
                     <div class="ZazzleTemplateFieldsUi-items" id="page_product_template-items">
                      <script language="javascript" type="text/jst">
                       [% /* &lt;![CDATA[ */ %]
							[%
								var
									templateFields = input.templateFields,
									itemNo = -1,
									templateFieldsLength = templateFields.length
								;

								for (; ++itemNo &lt; templateFieldsLength;) {
									var field = templateFields[itemNo];
									var widgetName = 'item' + itemNo;

									if (field.ppShow != false) {
							%]

									&lt;div class="ZazzleTemplateFieldsUi-item ZazzleTemplateFieldsUi-[%= field.type %] ZazzleWidgetsSppTemplate-[%= field.type %]"&gt;
										[% if (field.nameVerbose) { %]
											&lt;label
												id="page_product_template_elements_[%= widgetName %]-label"
												for="page_product_template_elements_[%= widgetName %]-input"
												class="ZazzleTemplateFieldsUi-itemLabel"
											&gt;[%= field.nameVerbose %]:&lt;/label&gt;
										[% } %]
										&lt;div class=""&gt;
											[%
												if (field.type == 'text') {
													if (field.value.indexOf('\n') == -1) {
											%]
												



&lt;span id="page_product_template_elements_[%= widgetName %]" class="ZazzleTextInput"&gt;
	

	
		&lt;input
			id="page_product_template_elements_[%= widgetName %]-input"
			class="ZazzleTextInput-input ZazzleTemplateFieldsUi-textFieldInput"
			name="[%= field.name %]" 
			type="text"
			maxlength="512" style="width:95%;" value="[%= field.value %]" 
		/&gt;
	
&lt;/span&gt;
											[%
													}
													else {
											%]
												



&lt;span id="page_product_template_elements_[%= widgetName %]" class="ZazzleTextInput"&gt;
	

	
		&lt;textarea
			id="page_product_template_elements_[%= widgetName %]-input"
			class="ZazzleTextInput-input ZazzleTemplateFieldsUi-textFieldInput"
			name="[%= field.name %]" maxlength="512" style="width:95%;height:60px;" 
		&gt;[%= field.value %]&lt;/textarea&gt;
	
&lt;/span&gt;
											[%
													}
												}
												else {
											%]
												

&lt;div id="page_product_template_elements_[%= widgetName %]" class="ZazzleImageSelectorSingle ZazzleImageSelectorSingle"&gt;
	
	
	&lt;div id="page_product_template_elements_[%= widgetName %]-outerBorder" class="ZazzleImageSelectorSingle-outerBorder" style="width:116px; height:116px;"&gt;
		&lt;div
			id="page_product_template_elements_[%= widgetName %]-preview"
			class="ZazzleImageSelectorSingle-preview ZazzleImageSelectorSingle-linearGradient"
			style=;
			margin:0.5em;"
		&gt;
			&lt;div class="ZazzleImageSelectorSingle-tableReset"&gt;
				&lt;div class="ZazzleImageSelectorSingle-centering"&gt;
